        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Torch张量语法"><a href="#Torch张量语法" class="headerlink" title="Torch张量语法"></a>Torch张量语法</h1><h2 id="1-使用索引来对张量切片，共用一段内存地址，类似于指针的操作"><a href="#1-使用索引来对张量切片，共用一段内存地址，类似于指针的操作" class="headerlink" title="1. 使用索引来对张量切片，共用一段内存地址，类似于指针的操作"></a>1. 使用索引来对张量切片，共用一段内存地址，类似于指针的操作</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 共用内存的赋值方法</span>point <span class="token operator">=</span> points<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 不适用共用内存,开辟新内存</span>point <span class="token operator">=</span> points<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>clone<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="2-storage方法"><a href="#2-storage方法" class="headerlink" title="2. storage方法"></a>2. storage方法</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 获取张量之间的排列,为连续的内存空间</span>points<span class="token punctuation">.</span>storage<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 获取tensor第一个元素和storage第一个元素间的偏移量</span>points<span class="token punctuation">.</span>storage_offset<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="3-stride方法"><a href="#3-stride方法" class="headerlink" title="3. stride方法"></a>3. stride方法</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python">point <span class="token operator">=</span> torch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>ones<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>point<span class="token punctuation">.</span>stride<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 通过这种方式可以拿到数据的内存之间的偏移地址,返回值为Tuple</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># stride()会返回第i层+1和第i层之间所经过的内存偏移</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 此例子中 为(20, 5, 1)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="4-转置方法"><a href="#4-转置方法" class="headerlink" title="4. 转置方法"></a>4. 转置方法</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python">points <span class="token operator">=</span> points<span class="token punctuation">.</span>t<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>points <span class="token operator">=</span> points<span class="token punctuation">.</span>transpose<span class="token punctuation">(</span>dim1<span class="token punctuation">,</span> dim2<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 注意的是 转置后内存地址不变</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 实质上,只是反转了stride中的步长,从而改变索引 </span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="5-数据类型"><a href="#5-数据类型" class="headerlink" title="5. 数据类型"></a>5. 数据类型</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python">torch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>doubletorch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>floattorch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>inttorch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>bool<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 具体方法</span>point<span class="token punctuation">.</span>to <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#(对应类型)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="6-索引方法"><a href="#6-索引方法" class="headerlink" title="6. 索引方法"></a>6. 索引方法</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 索引方式同 python 数组 [beg, end, step]</span>points<span class="token punctuation">[</span>none<span class="token punctuation">]</span>   <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 相当于给向量升一个维度</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="6-数组之间的切换"><a href="#6-数组之间的切换" class="headerlink" title="6. 数组之间的切换"></a>6. 数组之间的切换</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python">a <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 数组转化为np数组</span>b <span class="token operator">=</span> np<span class="token punctuation">.</span>array<span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 数组(python数组和np数组均可)转化为torch张量</span>c <span class="token operator">=</span> torch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>tensor<span class="token punctuation">(</span>b<span class="token punctuation">,</span> device <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'cuda:0'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>to<span class="token punctuation">(</span>torch<span class="token punctuation">.</span>int<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="7-连续化"><a href="#7-连续化" class="headerlink" title="7. 连续化"></a>7. 连续化</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python">points1 <span class="token operator">=</span> points<span class="token punctuation">.</span>contiguous<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 对于转置得到的数组,连续化操作之后可以得到连续内存空间的新张量</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
